Phase	Trigger	Duration	Key Activities
Confusion	Session start	3-5 turns	Observe, ask questions, feel out the room
Recognition	Identify 2+ entities	4-6 turns	Name entities, test hypotheses, verify tells
Negotiation	Know half the room	3-5 turns	Set boundaries, establish protocols, redirect
